Bachelor topic title:
    Web application for Online Business Promotion

Description of the problem:
    The users will have the ability to add liked business in a liked services list towards
    benefiting by some functionalities. The application should display this selected services in
    a different way.

Advantages:
    - the extension of certain objects is dynamically made, at run-time
    - multiple decoration can be easily implemented
    - the decoration is transparent

Disadvantages:
    - can generate multiple objects which may look the same, but have different behaviors
      which will result a code difficult to understand
    - a decorator wraps the objects, therefore is not identical with the initial objects

